OL,6,FA funeral director said he has
OL,7,Freceived many concerned calls from the
OL,8,Fpublic and families of people they
OL,9,Fhave buried, after they have been
OL,10,Fconfused with the business of a
OL,11,Fsimilar name currently under
OL,12,Finvestigation in Hull.
OL,14,FLegacy Funeral Services has been
OL,15,Foperating in since 2019.
OL,17,FSince last week, several families have
OL,18,Fbeen in contact with him under the
OL,19,Fassumption it is connected to one
OL,20,Fcalled Legacy Independent Funeral
OL,21,FDirectors.
