OL,6,FThat Yorkshire based business is being
OL,7,Finvestigated by Humberside Police with
OL,8,F35 people and a "quantity" of
OL,9,Fsuspected ashes have been recovered by
OL,10,Fofficers over "concern for care of the
OL,11,Fdeceased".
OL,13,F, fraud by false representation and
OL,14,Ffraud by abuse of position have been
OL,15,Freleased on bail, the force said.
OL,17,FJames Burrett, Director at the firm in
OL,18,FAylesbury, said he received multiple
OL,19,Fcalls from worried families as well as
OL,20,Festablished clients, which thought it
OL,21,Fwas related to the one in Yorkshire.
