OL,6,F"As a company you work so hard to make
OL,7,Fsure you have the trust of the local
OL,8,Fcommunity," said Mr Burrett.
OL,10,F"The main point is we're upset for the
OL,11,Ffamilies and what they had to go
OL,12,Fthrough. These families don't deserve
OL,13,Fthis, they're going through a time of
OL,14,Fgrief. It's the last thing they need
OL,15,Fat this time is this."
OL,17,FHe told ITV News Meridian that lots of
OL,18,Fpeople they have looked after in the
OL,19,Fpast "may have questions", but he
OL,20,Fwants to assure the public that the
OL,21,Ftwo companies are not related.
