OL,6,FA Government spokesperson said: "In
OL,7,Ftimes of great personal loss every
OL,8,Ffamily rightly expects their loved
OL,9,Fones are treated with dignity and
OL,10,Frespect and the government is working
OL,11,Fwith the funeral sector to ensure this
OL,12,Fis the case.
OL,14,F"We are currently reviewing regulation
OL,15,Fof the funeral sector and, in the
OL,16,Finterim, we support the work of the
OL,17,Ftrade bodies who have introduced self-
OL,18,Fregulation, including codes of
OL,19,Fpractice designed to regulate funeral
OL,20,Fdirectors."
